    <item>
      <title>英国承受全球债券抛售的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-01-09/britain-takes-the-heat-from-a-global-bond-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在其他条件相同的情况下，利率上升通常会导致货币走强。然而，本周英国政府债券收益率飙升的同时，英镑却出现下滑，这可能表明，由于投资者担心持续的通胀压力和财政可持续性，资本外逃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-01-09/britain-takes-the-heat-from-a-global-bond-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 11:19:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰启动 2025 年外汇债券发售，以满足创纪录的融资需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/poland-starts-2025-fx-debt-sales-to-fill-record-funding-needs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰即将启动今年首次外币债券发售，旨在满足创纪录的融资需求，并加入美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普上任前新兴市场债券发行热潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/poland-starts-2025-fx-debt-sales-to-fill-record-funding-needs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 11:07:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰能源集团 Orlen 在业绩平淡的一年后提高 2035 年计划中的股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/polish-energy-group-orlen-boosts-dividends-in-2035-plan-after-lackluster-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰最大的能源公司 Orlen SA 计划在未来十年增加股息并向清洁能源投资高达 910 亿美元，以在去年股价暴跌后重新赢得投资者的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/polish-energy-group-orlen-boosts-dividends-in-2035-plan-after-lackluster-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 09:59:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国市场抛售加剧，英镑跌至年内最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/pound-slumps-to-weakest-since-2023-amid-broad-uk-market-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心借贷成本飙升导致工党政府难以控制赤字，英镑跌至一年多来的最低点，股市下跌，英国政府债券连续第四天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/pound-slumps-to-weakest-since-2023-amid-broad-uk-market-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 07:04:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国债券市场动荡令人回想起1976年债务危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/uk-bond-turmoil-gives-labour-nightmare-of-britain-s-1976-debt-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最近的债券风暴让人联想到 2022 年利兹·特拉斯 (Liz Truss) 的迷你预算灾难，但将其与 20 世纪 70 年代的债务危机进行比较可能更为恰当。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/uk-bond-turmoil-gives-labour-nightmare-of-britain-s-1976-debt-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金持稳，因交易员关注可能影响利率路径的美国数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/gold-holds-two-day-gain-before-us-data-that-may-shape-rate-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于本周晚些时候将公布关键就业数据，交易员们正在考虑美联储的宽松路径前景，黄金价格连续两天上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/gold-holds-two-day-gain-before-us-data-that-may-shape-rate-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 00:15:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国债结束四天抛售；英国资产暴跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受全球债券需求强劲信号的影响，美国国债本周首日上涨，结束了因投资者对政府债务和通胀上升的担忧而引发的抛售。英国资产继续遭受重创。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 22:28:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Codelco 利用债务市场为创纪录的铜矿支出提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/codelco-taps-debt-market-to-fund-record-copper-mine-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利国有铜业公司 Codelco 发行了 15 亿美元债券，以筹集创纪录的投资，从而保持其作为全球最大铜生产商的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/codelco-taps-debt-market-to-fund-record-copper-mine-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 18:11:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
